      "text": "Highlights\n• MISO’s market efficiencies and regional coordination delivered an estimated $5.1 billion in annual \nbenefits, with cumulative benefits surpassing $50 billion since 2007. For every dollar spent on MISO \nmembership, participants realize $15 in benefits.\n• MISO’s co-optimized energy and ancillary services markets enhanced grid efficiency in 2024, \nincorporating new forecasting methods and updated reserve strategies to drive greater operational \nperformance. \n• By leveraging one of the largest geographic footprints for energy coordination, MISO enables its \nmembers to reduce reserve margins, optimize renewables and avoid unnecessary infrastructure \ninvestments – delivering sustained value in a dynamic energy environment.\nMISO VALUE PROPOSITION\nANNUAL VIEW\nContents\nPurpose of the Value Proposition.............................................................................................................1\nImproved Reliability ....................................................",
      "highlights": [
